= Story Guide =

'''Dragon Warrior III''' follows the child of the hero Ortega on a quest to defeat the Archfiend Baramos.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

Ortega, the greatest warrior of Aliahan, fell in battle against Baramos the Archfiend. Now his child comes of age and must complete the quest to save the world.

