== The Quest for Baramos ==

=== Ramia ===

With all six orbs:
# Go to the Shrine
# Revive the bird Ramia
# Fly to Baramos's Castle

=== Baramos's Castle ===

The Archfiend's fortress:
* Located on unreachable landmass
* Requires Ramia to reach
* Multiple dungeon floors

=== Defeating Baramos ===

The Archfiend awaits:
* Powerful magic attacks
* High HP
* Bring plenty of healing

After defeating Baramos, return victorious... but the story isn't over.

== The Dark World ==

=== The Twist ===

After Baramos's defeat:
# Return to Aliahan
# Celebrate victory
# Zoma appears - the true enemy
# World pit opens
# Descend to Alefgard

=== Alefgard ===

A dark version of Dragon Warrior I's world:
* Tantegel Castle
* Rimuldar
* Hauksness
* All familiar locations

